#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn23.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn23.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 23 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 23 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamamāravagga "
msgstr "1. About Māra "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn23.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Pariññeyyasutta "
msgstr "4. Should Be Completely Understood "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn23.4:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.4:1.2"
msgid "Āyasmā rādho yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ rādhaṃ bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Rādha went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one side. The Buddha said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn23.4:2.1"
msgid "“Pariññeyye ca, rādha, dhamme desessāmi pariññañca pariññātāviṃ puggalañca. "
msgstr "“Rādha, I will teach you the things that should be completely understood, complete understanding, and the person who has completely understood. "

msgctxt "sn23.4:2.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇāhi, sādhukaṃ manasi karohi; bhāsissāmī”ti. "
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention, I will speak.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.4:2.3"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho āyasmā rādho bhagavato paccassosi. "
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” Rādha replied. "

msgctxt "sn23.4:2.4"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.4:2.5"
msgid "“katame ca, rādha, pariññeyyā dhammā? "
msgstr "“And what things should be completely understood? "

msgctxt "sn23.4:2.6"
msgid "Rūpaṃ kho, rādha, pariññeyyo dhammo, vedanā pariññeyyo dhammo, saññā pariññeyyo dhammo, saṅkhārā pariññeyyo dhammo, viññāṇaṃ pariññeyyo dhammo. "
msgstr "Form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness. "

msgctxt "sn23.4:2.7"
msgid "Ime vuccanti, rādha, pariññeyyā dhammā. "
msgstr "These are called the things that should be completely understood. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.4:2.8"
msgid "Katamā ca, rādha, pariññā? "
msgstr "And what is complete understanding? "

msgctxt "sn23.4:2.9"
msgid "Yo kho, rādha, rāgakkhayo dosakkhayo mohakkhayo—"
msgstr "The ending of greed, hate, and delusion. "

msgctxt "sn23.4:2.10"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, rādha, pariññā. "
msgstr "This is called complete understanding. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.4:2.11"
msgid "Katamo ca, rādha, pariññātāvī puggalo? "
msgstr "And what is the person who has completely understood? "

msgctxt "sn23.4:2.12"
msgid "‘Arahā’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "It should be said: a perfected one, "

msgctxt "sn23.4:2.13"
msgid "Yvāyaṃ āyasmā evaṃnāmo evaṅgotto—"
msgstr "the venerable of such and such name and clan. "

msgctxt "sn23.4:2.14"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, rādha, pariññātāvī puggalo”ti. "
msgstr "This is called the person who has completely understood.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn23.4:2.15"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

